+------------+--------------+------------------+
study_sessions table:

+------------+------------+------------+--------------+---------------+
| session_id | student_id | subject    | session_date | hours_studied |
+------------+------------+------------+--------------+---------------+
| 1          | 1          | Math       | 2023-10-01   | 2.5           |
| 2          | 1          | Physics    | 2023-10-02   | 3.0           |
